You better not play tricks.

28
00:02:33,762 --> 00:02:35,418
Qiu Shui.

29
00:02:36,022 --> 00:02:40,221
Chao Ran, Yu Han, let's go upstairs
and detoxify Mr. Feng.

30
00:02:43,462 --> 00:02:46,710
Fang, help Qiu Shui

31
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:49,282
remove that Silver Butterfly Dart.

32
00:03:00,262 --> 00:03:02,970
- Let's go.
- Move.

33
00:03:07,326 --> 00:03:09,178
Let's begin.

34
00:03:10,582 --> 00:03:13,498
Let's talk before removing the dart.

35
00:03:16,121 --> 00:03:18,702
There's nothing to discuss.

36
00:03:18,702 --> 00:03:21,402
Fine. Let's skip the chat then.

37
00:03:28,290 --> 00:03:29,661
I'm warning you.

38
00:03:29,661 --> 00:03:32,742
My brother Rou is naive
and doesn't read people well.

39
00:03:32,742 --> 00:03:37,381
He admires you. You must've fooled him thoroughly.

40
00:03:37,381 --> 00:03:39,841
I don't care what happened between you two,

41
